* Listed among the 2011 Greenest Vehicles of the Year by the [[American Council for an Energy-Efficient Economy]].<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.greenercars.org/Green%20Book%202011%20Press%20FINAL.pdf |title=Latest Technology Place but Don't Win in this Year's Greenest Vehicles List |work=GreenCars.org |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2011-02-15 |accessdate=2011-02-15 |url-status = dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110303151005/http://greenercars.org/Green%20Book%202011%20Press%20FINAL.pdf |archivedate=2011-03-03 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.plugincars.com/chevy-volt-barely-makes-2011-list-top-12-greenest-vehicles-106816.html|title=Chevy Volt Barely Makes 2011 List of Greenest Vehicles|work=PluginCars.com |last=Berman |first=Brad |date=2011-02-15|accessdate=2011-02-15}}</ref>
