== {{anchor|M400}} Fourth generation (M400; 2016–present) == {{Infobox automobile | name = Fourth generation (M400) | image = %2716 Chevrolet Spark (SIAM 2016).jpg | aka = {{unbulleted list | Chevrolet Beat
