By April 2016, cumulative sales of cars of the Cruze name exceeded 4 million worldwide.<ref name=4miCruze>{{cite pr|url=https://media.chevrolet.com/media/us/en/chevrolet/news.detail.html/content/Pages/news/us/en/2016/apr/0418-cruze.html|title=2016 Chevrolet Cruze Offers 42 MPG on the Highway|date=18 April 2016|accessdate=13 January 2019|location=Detroit, Michigan|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170704150307/https://media.chevrolet.com/media/us/en/chevrolet/news.detail.html/content/Pages/news/us/en/2016/apr/0418-cruze.html|archivedate=4 July 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>

